BVB

4B Pots IP

4bet pot HJ vs LJ 25,60,x, all in

A+Broadway - high freq small bet
AAx - small/x 50/50
A+ <=9 - small/x 40/60
Mono - range check
Kxx General heuristic small range
Qxx straight possible - 50/50, small range
Jxx - FD - Range small, Rainbow - Range big if straight draws possible, otherwise range small
Txx - straight draws possible - T9x,T8x 60/x 80/20, rest range small
9xx and lower avg 80/20, good board 90/10, bad 70/30

BTN vs CO 4B sizes 25,60,x(,AI if used at all)

Axx on BTN vs CO is very atipical compared to the other spots, Axx means v high check frequency because of weighted Ax in BTN's call vs 4b range
A+broadway usually high bet small, A+lower card polarizing with 80%-90% check freq - can be simplified to range check
Kxx range small
Qxx range small
Jxx 60/x 80/20
Txx FD 60/x 70/30, r 100/0
9xx and lower 60/x 80/20

LJ vs BTN sizes 25,60,x(,AI if used at all)

Axx range small
Kxx range small
Qxx Some polarization on boards that contain 2x9,8,7 60/x 50/50 otherwise range small
JTx, J9x range small, lower 60/x 80/20
Txx simplify 60/x 70/30
9xx and lower A lot of mid cards - 60/x 50/50 otherwise 80/20

CO vs LJ 4B sizes 25,60,x(,AI if used at all)

Axx Range small, some checking when mid cards present 6-T
Kxx Range small
Qxx range small, when straight possible 60/x 50/50
Jxx Range small FD, rainbow range big
Txx 60/x 80/20 avg
9xx and lower if many mid cards/straight present 60/x 50/50 otherwise 80/20
